Feature: Use Fitness Band
  As a user
  I want to use a Fitness Band

    @storykey=FIT-2
    @testcasekey=FIT-TC-301
    Scenario: Set device on Run mode 
    Given I run for 30 minutes
    When I check the device 
    Then I burn 100 calories
	
    @storykey=FIT-2
    @testcasekey=FIT-TC-302
    Scenario: Set device on Walk mode
 	  Given I walk for 1 hour
	  When I check the device 
	  Then I burn 200 calories
	
